= Zvent 0.0.1

An interface with zvents API without all the mess.

== Description

An interface with zvents API without all the mess.

== Usage

#give it yoru API key
@zvent = Zvent::Sesion.new('API_KEY')

# Get an event
# give it the event id
event = @zvent.find_event('12345')
#returns: <Zvent::Event:0x13d8884>

# Each event has a venue object
event.venue
#returns <Zvent::Venue:0x13d8bf4>


# Search for Events
# give it a location
events = @zvent.find_events('Simi Valley, CA')
#returns {:events => [<Zvent::Event:0x13d8884>, ...],
#					:event_count => 10}

